{
  "stem": "4361.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, OK, so Hitler got this chunk of-- of-- of Czechoslovakia, Sudetenland, so that's going to keep him happy and peace.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, I mean, human beings are human beings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, this was the, the almost pathetic naivete of the people in my town, or to be more specific, my family, my father not reading the script correctly.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The script he was reading was probably denial of reality.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although in those days, he wasn't alone in denying reality because Chamberlain, the premier of-- of England, went back with a piece of paper.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and he said, 'Peace in our time,' famous last words.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father was not the only one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the general belief, that, you know, this madness cannot last, particularly when there were-- the news came that in Germany butter was ersatz butter and ersatz coffee.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, I mean, a civilized people will not stand for this kind of a mad dictator.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By this time, Hitler wasn't only a madman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was also referred to more or less as 'the mad dictator.' How and when did it start changing for you?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For me, it started to change when the Hungarians occupied my town, or 2/5 of Transylvania.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was already in 1940.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Second World War was declared in 1939.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the concept of 'blitzkrieg' or the, the-- not the concept, but rather the word, the idea of 'blitzkrieg' was introduced when Hitler occupied Poland in a matter of weeks.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then war broke out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, he declared war on France on May 1940.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on August 1940, there was a conference in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was called, I believe, the Second Award Conference, in which, in which Hungary, Romania were part of.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
